{"id": 1583, "genre": 1000, "title": "你受够了哪些奋力宣扬城市形象的手段？", "description": "人爱为自己脸上贴金，城市也是一样。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 14989, "comment_count": 66, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170323105238aKEmq5pzeYJunDMZ.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-03-23T17:00:56Z", "questions": [{"id": 2052, "title": "你受够了哪些奋力宣扬城市形象的手段？", "content": "你都见过哪些宣扬“城市形象”的手段？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 182378, "content": "靠申办马拉松来“打造”“国际化都市”", "image": "img/option/option/20170322213758uCkqzPwKn2FVQxOJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 182379, "content": "自然资源并不出色，使劲新种了一批树赶趟儿开办各种花节", "image": "img/option/option/20170322213930hQuI4tweWfMRlr8D.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 182380, "content": "难辨真假地以“名人恋爱、写作、发疯的地方”为卖点", "image": "img/option/option/20170323100651WoPyt2TxVfmiFQM9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 182381, "content": "申办“国际峰会”，然后房价因此涨了非常多", "image": "img/option/option/2017032310154340fLOKBvpMlxeR3P.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 182382, "content": "人文气息速成，开办质量并不值得称道的音乐节、展览会等", "image": "img/option/option/201703231035365d91nTvlY2X3MCZP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 182383, "content": "装一排智能路灯就宣传诸如“智慧城市”概念", "image": "img/option/option/20170323103804BT9QXRvKeHcVnk6u.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 182384, "content": "不管有没有条件都仿古，拆掉正常街区，复制第n个古镇", "image": "img/option/option/20170323104219XlDiV4c3vIWC8TeE.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}